# Product: FridgeWise (or your app name)

## Problem
Users don't know what's in their fridge. Perishables expire before they're used,
costing money and creating waste.

## Solution
Users log their fridge inventory. The app recommends recipes based on what they have.

## Versions
- V1: Manual inventory input + recipe suggestions
- V2: Camera-based fridge scanning (image recognition)

## Target User
Anyone with a fridge. No cooking expertise assumed.

## Core User Flow
1. User adds inventory (manually or via photo)
2. App surfaces recipe suggestions from available ingredients
3. User accepts a recipe → inventory is deducted automatically

## Design Constraint
Must be fully usable on both mobile and desktop.